			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>I'm talking about Goat Simulator. Wait, stop, don't close the thread tab. I'm serious! Well I'm a little serious. I almost hate to spoil it, but it's like Katamari Damacy. Except with a goat. It's hilarious. This is the kind of game you give to a friend as a prank, only to find them still playing it hours later.<br />
<br />
And what's more, the trailer is brilliant. Game of the Year. Game of Every Year. Game of Forever.<br />
<br />

